    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Technical term used in wood pulp and paper research that refers to the stiffening of the polymer structure that takes place in lignocellulosic materials upon drying or water removal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
